projects.name: StoryTime Books
projects.description:
Contributors: Seokwoo Ha, Ethan Hutchison, and myself
Inspiration: Semester project
What it does: E-Commerce book store with admin dashboard
How I built it: Vue.js, Laravel backend, MySQL database running on AWS
Challenges I ran into: All new technologies for me and my team; We were sent home shortly after the project began due to COVID-19; communication; Making the project fully in SPA design
Accomplishments that I'm proud of: Great UI, fully functional, won best project in the class during presentation, all data is secure and protects from SQL Injection
What's next for StoryTimeBooks: We have many features we hope to add in the future.
